title: Singapore welcomes WSM delegates (APO - Asian Productivity Organization)
text: ( Source : APO - Asian Productivity Organization ) The 56th Workshop Meeting of Heads of NPOs ( WSM ) convened in Singapore from 20 to 22 October 2015 . It was attended by 35 NPO and agriculture delegates and 19 advisers representing APO members
